<ul>
<li>enabled: 此方启用与否，默认为<code v-pre>true</code>。若为<code v-pre>false</code>，则此方废。</li>
<li>type: 丹方之类，&quot;shaped&quot;为有序，&quot;shapeless&quot;为无序。</li>
<li>XXX YYY ZZZ乃合成所需之物也。</li>
<li>ingredients: 丹方之材列。<code v-pre>X</code>、<code v-pre>Y</code>、<code v-pre>Z</code>乃材料之简称。</li>
<li>result: 成品。<code v-pre>material</code>为成品之基材。</li>
</ul>
<QuestionBlock title="有序与无序，其别安在？">
<p>以<strong>金刚之剑</strong>为例，其排列须<strong>精确</strong>。</p>
<div class="language- line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34"><pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code" v-pre=""><code class="language-"><span class="line"><span>工作台布局：</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>[ ] [D] [ ]</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>[ ] [D] [ ]</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>[ ] [S] [ ]</span></span>
<span class="line"><span></span></span>
<span class="line"><span>D = 钻石</span></span>
<span class="line"><span>S = 木棍</span></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>此即<strong>有序之合</strong>。
而若骨粉之属，<strong>随处置格皆可成者，则为无序之合</strong>。</p>
</QuestionBlock>
